{"tid":1992611,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(理性討論) 點解要ban考警?","createTime":"2020-04-28T08:58:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-29T00:34:43.000Z","uid":306427,"like":2,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"c17da507636975dcecb86e43106f520523d9b9c1","tid":1992611,"uid":306427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T08:58:05.000Z","msg":"其實點解要ban考警呢個方法? 你同路人考到入去就有機會做到改變(就算可能好小嘅改變都好) 但係冇同路人入去嘅話 狗隊就永遠都係狗隊 唔會有改變 <br />\n<br />\n唔except幾年內就可以突然大改革到 但點解唔嘗試去慢慢改變? 點解唔係有機會就嘗試下先而係直接ban<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好同我講14年雨革後入去個班點點點 宜家打得最勁個班一定係14年黃個班? 就算係 失敗左一次就直接ban? 如果係嘅話 街頭勇武抗爭夠失敗左好多次 點解仲要繼續 究竟考警呢個方法係有乜問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申: 想認真理性討論 要屈毛屈蛇就自便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0bcc544d2a72afa54e641e6f2d300d2957e1222","tid":1992611,"uid":69741,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T09:00:12.000Z","msg":"14年都有人咁講，19年一係同化，一係辭職<br />\n此po已完"},{"pid":"890fe9f1fd99669faddc7aa429a3192072e7abd5","tid":1992611,"uid":235316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T09:00:16.000Z","msg":"[行動po]香港人日程表更新<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1992311\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1992311</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"389e60a1ffe7c9312a1e5947995ad7182027187b","tid":1992611,"uid":73565,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T09:01:04.000Z","msg":"你會唔會加入黑社會再帶佢地從良"},{"pid":"892b16663a373d1fd48b8500ee0b9eda260897a5","tid":1992611,"uid":57674,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T09:01:25.000Z","msg":"因為14年到19年證明左係唔WORK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人性"},{"pid":"88f6481474821cf97c1fa4a58fe0e6f0f289c725","tid":1992611,"uid":78465,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T09:02:05.000Z","msg":"全民加入共產黨囉"},{"pid":"6e7eeeed87cb0d0a12a4af0be39556